subject: United States Open (Tennis)
Taxicabs and Taxicab Drivers
Labor and Jobs
Economic Conditions and Trends
lead_paragraph: Dispatchers say demand for for-hire cars, called black cars by their drivers, is half of what it was a year or two ago in New York City and at the United States Open.
